      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Unbridled Mayhem",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "\u003CPL\u003E, a mission\r\nfrom Master Arlow. With much\r\ndelight, he\u0027s gathered some\r\nferocious and lively beasts for\r\nyou to hunt. Make your way\r\nto the Arena when you\u0027re ready.",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Ravage incontr\u00F4l\u00E9",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "\u003CPL\u003E, une mission de\r\nMa\u00EEtre Arlow t\u0027attend. Il est\r\nravi d\u0027avoir rassembl\u00E9 des\r\nmonstres f\u00E9roces \u00E0 chasser\r\npour toi. Rends-toi \u00E0 l\u0027Ar\u00E8ne\r\nlorsque tu auras fini de\r\nte pr\u00E9parer.",
